Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:21.83,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}Living through these meaningless days, I let out a sigh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:29.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}I've lost sight of my true self
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:36.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Even if I strain my ears I can't hear your voice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:43.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}So I keep walking trying to catch up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:50.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}The things I couldn't tell you form into a chrysalis over time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:58.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,300)}Spreading wings, they take flight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:06.00,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}The one, the one precious thing I'll never forget
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:13.97,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Someday, that warm emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:19.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}I'll do what little I can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:28.57,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\c&H98ADF1&}Little by little, to get through to you
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.78,0:01:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It just started raining all of a sudden!{CPS}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.12,0:01:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume, let's hide under that roof.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.45,0:01:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a really big house.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.75,0:01:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of those old mansions, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.46,0:01:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.47,0:01:56.55,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to go near a place that I can sense demons from.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.97,0:02:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I just heard a weird voice from inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.56,0:02:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A voice?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.44,0:02:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanuma, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.11,0:02:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.86,0:02:13.40,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, no. The demon's coming out!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.11,0:02:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume{**-kun} and Tanuma{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.58,0:02:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.16,0:02:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And {*}Master Nyanko{**Nyanko-sensei}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:29.30,title-shadow,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}The Thing Lurking in the {\c&H8C769F&\4c&H8C769F&}Storeroom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.29,0:02:29.30,title,,0,0,0,,The Thing Lurking in the {\c&H035A08&}Storeroom
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.17,0:02:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is your house.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.22,0:02:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really big.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.01,0:02:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it's old and hard to clean.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.89,0:02:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why is {*}Master Nyanko{**Nyanko-sensei} here?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.43,0:02:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,After it started raining, I took a look outside...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.57,0:02:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluffy! Fluffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.82,0:02:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and the next thing I knew, I was holding onto him.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.49,0:02:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.74,0:02:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, when is she going to learn?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.20,0:03:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go thinking that a thin slice of jelly cake will make up for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.62,0:03:06.29,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, that demon's voice that I heard was just {*}Master{**Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.29,0:03:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to help me clean the storeroom?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.92,0:03:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,As thanks for the shelter.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.38,0:03:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. You're a big help.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.93,0:03:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Master Nyanko{**Nyanko-sensei}, do you sense any demons?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.85,0:03:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I guesh becaw 'f the famry's hishtory, I can feel the lethover presensh of lotsha demonsh,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.81,0:03:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but nut'ing particu'ry weirf.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.02,0:03:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.74,0:03:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got my jelly cake, so I'm going home.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.25,0:03:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.55,0:03:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,D-d-do...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.39,0:04:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That wooden doll wards off monsters, I heard.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.81,0:04:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really scared of it when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.56,0:04:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd scare off thieves, not just monsters.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.15,0:04:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your family used to be mediums, didn't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.57,0:04:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.78,0:04:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather researched demons,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.95,0:04:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,even though he couldn't see them.
