Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.66,0:04:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was young,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.29,0:04:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,he used to teach me all kinds of things in this storehouse.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But my mom and dad were both creeped out by it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.30,0:04:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who ever comes in here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.55,0:05:19.09,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A kappa, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.55,0:05:21.76,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he wanted to see demons,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.76,0:05:23.64,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he must have been a strange guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.10,0:05:28.35,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing good comes from seeing them.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.19,0:05:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How long is it going to take you to open that window?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That scared me...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.45,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimonos?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought somebody was standing there.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are for warding off monsters, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.71,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He really was strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.48,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.36,0:06:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the help!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.77,0:06:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I had no idea how hard it'd be.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.95,0:06:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can at least make you some food
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.16,0:06:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,as thanks for your work.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.95,0:06:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds great.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.25,0:06:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.55,0:06:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, did you put one of those kimonos away?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.22,0:06:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two, just like before.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.97,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But those two are kinda alike, aren't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.73,0:06:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're good friends, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.28,0:07:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They sound alike, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.53,0:07:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.86,0:07:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.20,0:07:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing... I'm just going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.21,0:07:17.38,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might be remembering it wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.08,0:07:21.05,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shouldn't scare them over nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.98,0:07:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.24,0:07:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.88,0:08:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, he saw me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He saw me! He saw me!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.59,0:08:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He saw me! He saw me!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.47,0:08:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.14,0:08:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen you before, kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.64,0:08:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can see demons?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.18,0:08:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're an interesting one.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.39,0:08:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you with that kimono demon?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just came over to visit.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.82,0:08:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When Shin'ichiro was alive,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here all the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.49,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, Taki's grandfather?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.49,0:08:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't see demons.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, he couldn't.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.83,0:08:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not 'til the very end.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that kimono demon?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.92,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You tore off that upside-down picture, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Like an upside-down Buddha,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.84,0:08:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you shouldn't touch anything you find that's upside down.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.30,0:08:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a spell called "Upside-Down Sealing".
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.68,0:09:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichiro did it once while reading from some old scrolls.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.06,0:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't know it, but the spell worked.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.73,0:09:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He sealed something really nasty here.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.45,0:09:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon in an old doll.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.66,0:09:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When it was sealed, its body was split,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.66,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}and the pieces were scattered all around the house.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.33,0:09:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Its torso and left hand were sealed in the storehouse.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.30,0:09:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be searching this house for the rest of its body.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.39,0:09:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If it gets it back, you're going to have a problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.73,0:09:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like its right leg is right under us.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.36,0:09:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.11,0:09:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This smell...
