Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.32,0:10:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.11,0:10:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something under the house?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.49,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A kimono monster, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.74,0:10:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather sealed it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.79,0:10:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.66,0:10:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Shin'ichiro's granddaughter?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.21,0:10:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something there?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.54,0:10:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah. It's the one who told me about the kimono demon.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.01,0:10:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a demon there?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.88,0:10:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She says that Shin'ichiro had a bit of potential, but he was never able to see her.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.10,0:11:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.06,0:11:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.65,0:11:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.11,0:11:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounded like something was crawling along the second floor.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.99,0:11:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.37,0:11:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It really does look like Natsume's acting weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.50,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.33,0:11:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we knew what was going on,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.34,0:11:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd know that he'd try to protect both us and this house.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.72,0:11:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.55,0:11:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.43,0:11:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This house has as many dark rooms as ever.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking from my shoulder.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.85,0:11:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You never played any tricks just because Shin'ichiro couldn't see you, did you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.77,0:11:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.82,0:11:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.78,0:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He really couldn't see us at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.66,0:12:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that window.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.16,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When Shin'ichiro was a child,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.33,0:12:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,he would always sit there, absorbed in old scrolls and books about demons.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.92,0:12:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He enjoyed them as though they were picture books.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.22,0:12:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.80,0:12:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could see them, just once.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.89,0:12:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so funny how he never realized that we were right there.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.86,0:12:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good times.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.20,0:12:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume{**_kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.50,0:12:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go up.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.67,0:12:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanuma?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.84,0:12:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.25,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But this feeling... there's something up here.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,On the right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.40,0:13:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh, he's here, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.16,0:13:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for grabbing you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.72,0:13:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you saved us.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.10,0:13:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.44,0:13:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, it's been a while since I've felt that strange spiritual energy.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.36,0:13:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The seal's broken?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.94,0:14:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I came because I was hoping Shin'ichiro got back and started something fun again.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.53,0:14:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichiro left this world a long time ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.50,0:14:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans can't come back to life easily.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.96,0:14:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. How boring.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.84,0:14:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.92,0:14:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wait, Shin'ichiro's right here!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is what they call a "granddaughter".
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.55,0:14:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the girl who wouldn't stop sobbing at Shin'ichiro's funeral.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.02,0:14:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.77,0:14:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How boring.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.23,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume{**-kun},
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.02,0:14:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of demons are over there?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.53,0:14:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They knew your grandfather,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.20,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and they really seemed to like the guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.41,0:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww... oww...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare say that!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He never even saw us!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.67,0:15:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichiro was just our plaything!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.34,0:15:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can see us?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How rare.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.97,0:15:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How different from Shin'ichiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, child of man,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.89,0:15:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall give you a warning since you can see us.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.81,0:15:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon standing on the wall said that the kimono demon was called "Kakura".
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten its legs and its left arm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Its right hand is broken and rotted,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.24,0:15:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and all that's left is the head.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.61,0:15:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the backyard?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.91,0:15:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.58,0:15:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.25,0:15:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanuma...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.62,0:15:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.04,0:15:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking you'd tell me to wait here or go home again.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.59,0:15:48.84,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.84,0:15:51.01,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are people who will listen to me,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.85,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and try to stay by my side anyway...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.36,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.36,0:16:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume{**-kun}!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.70,0:16:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.49,0:16:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that demon catch him?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to look for something we can't see?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.37,0:16:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.50,0:16:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use the circle.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.83,0:16:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The circle?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.58,0:16:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the one that lets you see demons inside it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.63,0:16:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.38,0:16:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If I use it, we might be able to get the demons that Natsume talked with to help us.
