Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.97,0:16:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(275,0)\i1}How dare you look at me, human.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.36,0:16:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(267,568)\i1}They really seemed to like the guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume, where are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.45,0:16:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.45,0:16:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I should ask you that, Ponta!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.16,0:17:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I came because he hasn't come home yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.00,0:17:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.67,0:17:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh demons, please help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.30,0:17:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where Natsume went!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.51,0:17:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.35,0:17:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.18,0:17:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.93,0:17:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponta came.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.39,0:17:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the backyard.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.06,0:17:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you go into the circle?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We had no reason to.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.32,0:17:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good comes from dealing with humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.75,0:17:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't wake up, it'll cut off your right arm.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.27,0:18:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.52,0:18:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The backyard.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.85,0:18:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.06,0:18:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't take that out with one hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.98,0:18:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... good.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.23,0:18:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But since you have strong spiritual energy,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.40,0:18:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll take your arm and make it its own.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.41,0:18:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch my dessert!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.13,0:18:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Master Nyanko{*Nyanko-sensei!}!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Master Nyanko{*Nyanko-sensei!}!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.93,0:18:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this house?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.06,0:18:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There are half-finished barriers everywhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.60,0:18:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That Shin'ichiro guy must've copied them from somewhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.69,0:18:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the problem with partially talented people.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.62,0:18:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume{**-kun}!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.66,0:18:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous! Stay back!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.58,0:19:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop moving around!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Master Nyanko{*Nyanko-sensei!}!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.84,0:19:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my... I can't bear to watch.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.81,0:19:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, get him.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.19,0:19:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.74,0:19:35.20,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.20,0:19:37.82,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichiro isn't reading his books,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.82,0:19:39.53,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,and he stopped drawing those strange pictures.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.53,0:19:42.24,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,It seems he's gotten sick.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.58,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,How boring.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.58,0:19:45.50,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.50,0:19:49.25,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,A person called a "doctor" put both ends of a string with some kind of cylinder on it to his ears,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.25,0:19:52.75,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,and tried to heal Shin'ichiro by hitting his body with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.38,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,It looks just like it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.38,0:19:57.51,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,Will this heal him?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.51,0:19:59.39,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,If a mere human can heal him,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.39,0:20:01.51,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,then we should be able to, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.27,0:20:05.39,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,Get better, Shin'ichiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.77,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,Geez, humans are so weak.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.77,0:20:08.94,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,Get better.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.94,0:20:10.86,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,Get better, Shin'ichiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.86,0:20:13.44,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,We'll be so bored without you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.44,0:20:16.49,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the one who wanted to see us?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.49,0:20:17.90,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,Get better.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.90,0:20:21.58,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,Get better!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.20,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.87,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.87,0:20:28.62,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are crying voices.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.67,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're crying heavily.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.67,0:20:32.63,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together, with a young Taki.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.38,0:20:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume{**-kun}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.05,0:20:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, you're awake.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.67,0:20:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanuma, Taki.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.18,0:20:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kakura?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.05,0:20:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I tossed him in a faraway ditch.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.31,0:20:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Master{*Sensei}...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.77,0:20:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.94,0:20:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.52,0:20:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never coming back.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.57,0:20:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are such trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.15,0:21:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The demons on the wall saved us.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.99,0:21:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't save anybody.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.70,0:21:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.99,0:21:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just a lot of interesting stuff here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.54,0:21:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not because it's Shin'ichiro's house...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.34,0:21:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming to see my grandfather.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.88,0:21:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, granddaughter of Shin'ichiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.55,0:21:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.98,0:21:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this smell?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.40,0:21:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of flower?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.28,0:21:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.15,0:21:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was crying at my grandfather's funeral,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.53,0:21:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I smelled a gentle, flowery scent.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.37,0:21:50.16,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did they realize...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.12,0:21:53.88,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}how sadly they called the name
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.88,0:21:57.84,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of the man who could never see them?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.51,0:22:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In seeing something, we meet it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.30,0:22:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you tell me?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.39,0:22:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,About the demons that you've met.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.48,0:22:17.32,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been through so many meetings and partings.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.19,0:22:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.82,0:22:22.11,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They were like a heavy secret,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.61,0:22:25.16,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but when I started to talk about them, they seemed to sparkle...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.32,0:22:28.37,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't put them into words.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:41.17,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Lining up the sparks of warmth I've lost one by one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.72,0:22:49.39,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Coming to the rainbow-colored pieces of you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.35,0:22:54.85,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I crack a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:08.53,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Not even knowing how to make memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:16.21,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Even when we took things too fast
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:24.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We were only going with the flow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:31.35,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}No matter where I go, even after this darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.64,0:23:37.48,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}How many times must I say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:44.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Shining with the flame of a young heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:50.66,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Those faraway pieces of you
