Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.42,0:24:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.46,0:24:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Matoba.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.88,0:24:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to steal the blood of demons?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.30,0:24:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.72,0:24:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We should stay away from him.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.13,0:24:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.01,0:24:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm still so fabulous.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:12.56,0:24:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your bad feeling was right!
